These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, classical, techno, jazz
4 different pets are kept: hamster, hedgehog, chinchilla, bird
1. the fan classical is between the fan funk and the owner of the hedgehog##2
2. the fan classical is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3
3. the fan classical is somewhere between the fan jazz and the fan funk##7
4. the owner of the hedgehog is in an even position##4
5. the fan jazz is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
6. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hamster##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Music-Genre   | techno | jazz       | classical | funk        |
| Pet      | chinchilla  | hedgehog | bird        | hamster |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, montecristo, bongani, game
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, kiwi, peach, tomato
1. the person eating tomato is somewhere between the person eating peach and the bongani-smoker##7
2. the game-smoker is somewhere to the left of the blend-smoker##5
3. the game-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person eating tomato##5
4. the montecristo-smoker is on the left of the game-smoker##1
5. the person eating tomato is between the person eating peach and the person eating kiwi##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Cigar     | bongani | montecristo       | game         | blend     |
| Food   | kiwi   | tomato | peach | artichoke |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-3::.
4 different games are played: bridge, mah-jongg, monopoly, billiard
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, swimming, golf, rugby
1. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
2. the person who's sport is rugby is somewhere between the person who's sport is swimming and the person who's sport is biathlon##7
3. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
4. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere between the person who's sport is rugby and the person playing mah-jongg##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Game   | mah-jongg | billiard | monopoly | bridge  |
| Sport   | golf | biathlon  | rugby   | swimming |

