.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
House: colonial, townhouse, ranch-style, palace
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, mystery, western, zombie
1. the person watching zombie movies is on the far left or far right##3
2. the colonial house is somewhere between the person watching mystery movies and the palace house##7
3. the ranch-style house is the person watching zombie movies##1
4. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
5. the townhouse house is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| House   | townhouse | colonial | palace       | ranch-style |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery      | martial-arts   | western | zombie  |

