.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-5::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: purple, apricot, coral, mauve
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, d&b, punk, metal
1. the fan metal is on the left or right of the person who likes apricot##3
2. the fan gospel is somewhere to the left of the fan d&b##5
3. the person who likes purple is on the right of the person who likes coral##1
4. the fan metal is somewhere between the person who likes apricot and the person who likes purple##7
5. the fan metal is on the left of the fan punk##1
6. the fan d&b is somewhere to the left of the fan metal##5
7. the person who likes apricot is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who likes purple is on the left or right of the person who likes coral##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Color         | coral | purple   | mauve | apricot |
| Music-Genre   | gospel      | d&b | metal      | punk |

