3. the havana-smoker is on the right of the person playing chess##1
4. the person playing chess is on the left of the person playing poker##1
5. the person playing scrabble is on the left or right of the siglo-smoker##3
6. the siglo-smoker is somewhere between the vegafina-smoker and the havana-smoker##7
7. the alhambra-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person playing poker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
