.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-7::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, chess, rock-climbing, dancing
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, motorbike, subway, ship
1. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person driving the ship is somewhere between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##7
5. the person driving the subway is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##5
6. the person driving the ship is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby          | dancing    | filmmaking   | chess | rock-climbing  |
| Transport   | quad-bike | subway | ship    | motorbike |

