.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, photography, fishing, writing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, r&b, metal, folk
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is somewhere between the fan dubstep and the person who's hobby is photography##7
2. the fan dubstep is on the right of the fan r&b##1
3. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
4. the fan r&b is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##5
5. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left or right of the fan metal##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |  4  |
| Hobby         | photography    | fishing | writing     | rock-climbing |
| Music-Genre   | metal | folk  | r&b | dubstep |

 